nz.ac.vuw.ecs.swen225.gp20.maze.event

Class MazeEventListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • nz.ac.vuw.ecs.swen225.gp20.maze.event.MazeEventListener
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    AnimationHandler, Gui, MazeEventListenerExample, SoundHandler, UndoRedoHandler

    public class MazeEventListener
extends java.lang.Object
    Base class for any Listeners of Maze. Not abstract as you may not want to override every method. Implements the Visitor Pattern: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Visitor_pattern
